a.xlink:title: Returns array of internal properties specific to the value type.
Like SetNativeDataProperty, but V8 will replace the native data property with a real data property on...
Sets a "data property" on the object template, see https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-object-type.
Sets an "accessor property" on the object template, see https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-object-type.
Adds a property to each instance created by this template.

Returns true if the function does nothing.
